text: The following is a list of programs featured on The N. This brand launched in 2002 as a joint venture between MTV Networks (owners of Nickelodeon) and Sesame Workshop. ==Programming block== The N launched on April 1, 2002 and closed on December 30, 2007. It aimed at tweens and teenagers. The channel aired on for 12 hours from 6 p.m. to 6 a.m. to its older audience. ===Original series=== MTV Networks and Sesame Workshop created a company, Noggin LLC, to produce original content for The N. In 2002, Sesame Workshop sold its stake in Noggin LLC, but it continued to co-produce content for The N. Title First air date Last air date Big Kids Girls v.
